    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A broad range of brownish, yellowish, or reddish colors resembling the colors of pigments called "earth color," which contain iron oxide and other substances.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000009521/Color: Universal Language and Dictionary (1976)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指一廣泛範圍的褐色、黃色或紅色色彩，色近於顏料「大地色」，此顏料包含氧化鐵與其他物質。

</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een uitgebreide reeks bruinachtige, geelachtige of roodachtige kleuren die lijken op de kleuren van de pigmenten 'aardkleur', die ijzeroxide en andere stoffen bevatten.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Uma ampla gama de cores amarronzadas, amareladas ou avermelhadas que lembram as cores de pigmentos chamados "cor terra", que contêm óxido de ferro e outras substâncias.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
